
---
## Steal Points
### Import Code
```

```

### Commands
```
!steal = Tied to Steal Points
```
### Editable Settings
`costToSteal` This is how many points its going to cost for you to attempt the steal. `maxSteal` This is the max amount you can steal `minSteal` This is the min amount you can steal `failChance` This is the chance you will fail all together, the higher the number the higher the chance of success.
> To have it successful every time have `failChance` set to 100. 
> 
> {.is-info}
### Example Usage
```
!steal TerrierDarts
```
---
## Set All Users Points
> This will edit the amount of `points` for everyone the bot has seen since based on the user data loaded from when you opened the bot or since the last save which ever is more recent. {.is-info}
### Import Code
```

```
### Commands
```
!setAllPoints = Tied to SetAllPointsTo
```
### Example Usage
```
!setAllPointsTo 5000
```
